HEADWORD: Hachure
<hw>Hach"ure</hw> <pr>(h⟦acr⟧ch"⟦usl⟧r)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.,
fr. <ets>hacher</ets> to hack. See <er>Hatching</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Fine
